Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stepped on...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.02,0:00:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,your shadow!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn to be "it"!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.03,0:00:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me! \NI'm a crabbity crab!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta catch the crab...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Step, step!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.54,0:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get Manaka back to normal?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.59,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get someone to be able to fall in love again?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.98,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible it will return when the time comes, and it's possible it may never return.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.91,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, you understand now, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are indeed some things in this world you cannot do anything about.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.71,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stepped on your shadow, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.98,0:00:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Step!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.60,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.89,0:00:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad asked me to pick something up for him.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at the fishery cooperative. Could you come help me?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.27,0:01:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need me too?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.85,0:01:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.18,0:01:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you keep an eye on Akira instead?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay! 'Kay, 'kay!
