Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit trying to act so grown-up.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.68,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.27,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you thought you'd try to save me from the situation, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been a real crybaby lately,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so {\i1}someone{\i0} has to act the adult here.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, she said...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.85,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,she wanted to tell me something as soon as we were done with the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.27,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering what it was, but I think...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,she was gonna ask Tsumugu out.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.55,0:03:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If she told {\i1}you{\i0} she wanted to talk \Nand made such a big deal out of it,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's pretty obvious to me the one Manaka-san wanted to ask out was...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it was me?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.41,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Definitely"...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk to everyone about what {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko} said.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.34,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Including Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.01,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka too?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if it were about me...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd want to know.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.21,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.95,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's "definitely" not gonna happen either?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ability to fall in love...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.71,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do \Nabout the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But we might be able to do something about Manaka's condition,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wanna try to think of a way.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this something you can just \Nthink up a solution to?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about someone's feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.68,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different from trying to find the sea village \Nor trying to wake up Mukaido.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't do something—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.25,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how much harm {\i1}is{\i0} there in not being able to fall in love?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka looks like she's having fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to bother her at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Chisaki?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I might...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,actually be a little relieved.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.00,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think that depends on the person.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's something we can all \Njust solve like we usually do—
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How self-centered can you be?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.53,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys think you can just decide someone's better off without the ability to love?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even asked Manaka-san about it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu-chan...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she's better off not knowing?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to act all mature!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a kid, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something wrong with you guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.44,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me sick.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this is pissing me off!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so stupid!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is really important!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone should be able to feel it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay leaving the others?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Stupid Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call him stupid!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just do that?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different when I say it!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have homework to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never understand her.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.26,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.77,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun wanted to come find you guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
