Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, Akira!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never going to make \Nit home with Akira in tow.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't so bad every now and then.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.25,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that shining thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.55,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a red-bellied sea slug.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, those are rare.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.67,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I told a red-bellied sea slug something once.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't quite remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this rock?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell a sea slug your feelings,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll tell you what will come of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.49,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it spits up a white rock,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your wish will come true.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean your feelings are true?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If your feelings are misplaced, \Nit'll spit up a black rock.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold on to this.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you take really good care of it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Manaka's rock.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a hunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the color and shape.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.57,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flat and looks clumsy.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocks can be clumsy?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.39,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka said she told the sea slug something but couldn't remember what it was, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, whatever \NManaka told the sea slug
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,has something to do with falling in love with someone.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just have to ask Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If her feelings were so strong that she talked to a sea slug about them,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll be able to remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If she has help from the person she loves,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll happen for sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if Manaka's ability to fall in love does come back...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.82,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.88,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.95,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying I can sort of understand where Kaname-san and Chisaki-san were coming from.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.27,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The "if I don't love anyone, \NI won't be sad" thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying that the other day—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,well, five years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,391)}If I don't love anyone, I won't be so sad!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.95,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I don't know what will happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Kaname and Chisaki said,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.88,0:09:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it might be easier if she doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing you guys, \NI think that's definitely wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who showed me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dummy!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.08,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.91,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all able to love Akari,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your butt's hanging out!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.11,0:09:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and look how happy you are now.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want her to remember
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what it feels like to love someone.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san, I went ahead and took my bath.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take one a little later.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.25,0:10:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep hearing the sound of waves in my head.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of waves?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.61,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why Hii-kun told me to take care of this rock.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.26,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.79,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying really hard to do something for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.91,0:10:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know why.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just ask him?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.21,0:10:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have told me already if he wanted to.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.75,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This rock is pretty,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I look at it, \Nthe world stops making sense,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.89,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manaka-san's ability to fall in love was taken away.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.65,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So where her love was,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there is now a hole,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it's screaming.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.73,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's screaming that it's lonely.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.99,0:11:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san, would it be okay \Nif I borrowed that rock?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything bad to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it so you can take \Neven better care of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better care of it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On my life!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're funny, Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when you were little, and now, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.85,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari is thinking of Manaka-san more than himself.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right before exams, and I'll probably be home late,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd make extra for dinner, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you keep eating your vegetables when you go back to the university.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get really wrapped up in something,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you forget to eat properly.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you sleep properly, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to just nap on the sofa or the floor.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't make you feel any less tired.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you didn't need to tell the others?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.73,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going back to the university. No need to make a big deal about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something too?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.15,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you feel relieved if you lost the ability to fall in love?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good with your hands, Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.43,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, last night,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.06,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.49,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wouldn't like to \Nlose the ability to fall in love.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to be able to love someone,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,even if they don't love you back.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,These last five years,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I studied so hard,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I'd cry now and then...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.95,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'd be easier for me if I lost the ability to love,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't be who I am right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask Kaname out!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how it turns out.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he rejects me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.56,0:13:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can come to terms with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my own problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sayu...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I'm on duty today!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to write in the log and take it to {replace}Sensei{Teach}.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Her own problem, huh...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.18,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Hikari and the others?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently they already went home.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.53,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.25,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the sea slug's rock?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.83,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Akari-san's pendant!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the one with all the shells.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.38,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The one you all helped me with.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.66,0:14:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to come back to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We all helped make it, didn't we?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try harder, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.93,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want to try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.28,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fscx53\fscy53\pos(535,478)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HC0&\alpha&HC0&}Emergency \N\N\N\NExit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.28,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fscx53\fscy53\pos(535,478)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H12&}Emergency \N\N\N\NExit
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I really can take better care of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose it, and I'll always have it close to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't lose it, huh...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miuna-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you're so pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so pretty, and nice, and fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have everything, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.07,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why you mustn't lose anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose it, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just giving it some water.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought I'd take these home.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Home?{so much METAL GEAR?! in this show}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.13,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There are limits to what we can research from here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the university.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.87,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At least wait until she gets her feelings back!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.33,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in love with you!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.83,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna do whatever I can to get back her ability to love!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were able to trigger her feelings...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Trigger her feelings?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to do that?{show her the fish, obv}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like take her on a date, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss her and hold her?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, some kinda pervert?!{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't feel that way about Mukaido.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just act like you do!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if it's a lie!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's me that Mukaido is in love with?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When she looks at you, \Nshe gets red in the face
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and says your name all sweet.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's proof that she loves me?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna doubt Manaka's feelings?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.03,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had five more years of \Nphysical development than you.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give up, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lie.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.86,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if Mukaido does love me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.93,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say you love her,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka might turn back to normal!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.19,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You should never play around \Nwith people's feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.39,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm in love with Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.18,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with Chisaki.{sorry, man. this is anime, which means she's standing behind you.}{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.14,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.17,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I lose her now...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hear it...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.27,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}like a voice dimly remembered from so long ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mukaido's Ena...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. It's more than that.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.27,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So many feelings drift through these waters.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have Ena! \NWhat the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.93,0:18:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.89,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can talk?{wow, he is now an unterwasserman}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.09,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what it feels like to have Ena.{the pleasure of being ena'd outside}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.89,0:19:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but will you let me go alone from here?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Alone?{snake! this is a swimming mission!}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've never even been to the village—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to face Chisaki properly. \NJust the two of us.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I can't move forward.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.87,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.53,0:20:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared to be alone in Shishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tsumugu?!{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here in Shishio, Tsumugu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I came after you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can breathe?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents hated the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.33,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They left behind Gramps, who wanted to stay by the sea, and went to the city.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.51,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to stay close by as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.20,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when Hikari mistakenly thought that Egawa and the others broke the Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, you found out the truth
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to defend Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}Because if everyone else finds out about this,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe how foolish you were.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikari will wind up looking like the bad guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.73,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't imagine how someone could make such a spectacle of themselves for others.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.47,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so quiet and calm,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.40,0:21:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet sometimes you become so fierce that I can't handle you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were just like the sea.
